# Contributor: Jakub Jirutka <jakub@jirutka.cz>
# Contributor: Shiz <hi@shiz.me>
# Contributor: Jeizsm <jeizsm@gmail.com>
# Contributor: Ariadne Conill <ariadne@dereferenced.org>
